    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以FinTech_TransactionQueue作为入口，通过CreateOrderCMD触发到OrderPending。那订单pending之后有哪些出口？是直接进入processing，还是有其他分支？",
      "elements_involved": [
