    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "Pending之后通过MarkAsProcessingCMD进入Processing状态。这里有个关键设计：Processing状态有三条出路——正常完成、取消、以及异常。特别是异常路径，我们需要支持从Error恢复。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MarkAsProcessingCMD",
        "OrderProcessing",
        "OrderCompleted",
        "OrderCancelled",
        "OrderError"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认了，Processing是核心枢纽。我注意到您提到MarkOrderCompleteCMD同时出现在两条路径上——既通向Completed，也通向Error？这看起来像是同一个命令触发不同结果。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MarkOrderCompleteCMD",
        "OrderProcessing",
        "OrderCompleted",
        "OrderError"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "对，MarkOrderCompleteCMD在成功时推进到Completed，但如果执行过程中系统异常，就会落入Error状态。这是业务上的容错设计。另外，Processing阶段用户还可以主动CancelOrderCMD，直接终结到Cancelled。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "MarkOrderCompleteCMD",
        "OrderCompleted",
