      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，我先把主体结构画出来：TransactionQueue → Pending → Processing，然后Processing分出三条线——Complete到Completed，Cancel到Cancelled，以及异常到Error。最后Error还需要一条恢复路径。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "FinTech_TransactionQueue",
        "OrderPending",
